      "content": "hey, i'm starting this new blog about lifestyle and professional growth for a global audience. i want to write a guide on what \"sophisticated\" and \"professional\" behavior actually looks like in a global setting. can u give me a rundown of the core standards for things like dress codes, dining etiquette, and how someone should carry themselves to be taken seriously in international business?",
